game.name: Taco Blaster
game.description:
Every gamer wants to try something different every day. We have today got you covered with a brand new action-packed challenge that is enough to give you a unique taste in gaming. The food will come to eat you and your job is to avoid them to survive for as long as possible. Will you able to handle that kind of challenge? If yes, Taco Blaster is the best thing to try right away. Your ship has now become a taco and you as a player have to shoot all the enemy tacos.

Control your taco with the help of arrow keys or tapping on the screen of your mobile phone! Test your skills and special abilities to survive for long and create your own high score! Go through the instructions first before entering this HTML5 fun food-style shooting challenge! Move the taco up and down to control the flying tacos that you see coming on your way! Do not forget to shoot at the obstacles to make your score and boost it.

All the food will come to you from the right screen. Your best high score will depend upon how long you will go while shooting a lot to the unwanted food. Do not bother if you get bored if we are happy to take you to a wider collection of free action-packed challenges that are free to play online without download. Our cool shooter games are meant for both boys and girls and playable on multiple latest browsers and devices.
